com.emc.storageos.model.block.export

Class ITLRestRep

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.storageos.model.block.export.ITLRestRep

  • public class ITLRestRep
extends java.lang.Object
    An object that represents a single export path between an initiator and a block object (volume or snapshot). When a volume is successfully exported to an initiator, there will be a minimum of one instance of ITLRestRep. When multi-pathing is used, there could be as many as the number of paths specified depending on the availability of storage ports.
